<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٢٧]</span> حَبيب <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سمِعَ مُوَرِّقًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عَنه قَتادةُ، مُنقطِعٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>في البَصْريِّينَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٢٨]</span> حَبِيبٌ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عَن أَبيهِ، سمِعَ النَّبيَّ -صلى اللَّه عليه وسلم-.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>رَوى عَنهُ ابنُهُ هِرْماسٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>العَنْبرِيُّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٢٩]</span> حَبِيبٌ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَنِ القاسِمِ، وزَيدِ بنِ أَسلَمَ، مُنقطِعٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>سمِعَ مِنهُ سُليْمانُ التَّيمِيُّ،<span class="c5"> وَقالَ:</span> حدَّثني <span class="c2">(٦)</span> حَبيبٌ، أنَّه سألَ عَطاءً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَلا أَدْري، هُو المُعَلِّمُ أَم لا؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>* * *<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
